Octavio H. SOTO-TORO, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4751 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 02, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The petition for belated appeal is dismissed as untimely. See Fla. R. App. P. 9.141 (c)(5)(A).

LaROSE, C.J., and CASANUEVAand SALARIO, JJ., Concur.
